subject: Olympic Games (1984)
Olympic Games
Alpine Skiing
lead_paragraph: Olympic gold medalist Joss Christensen and other skiers visited Sarajevo, Bosnia to explore, ski, and discover the ruins of a Winter Olympics 30-years old.
